     [38;2;248;248;242m[2m 2 [22m# AI Causal Analysis (Alpha)[2m[18;6H 3 [22mThe **AI Causal Analysis** calculator uses machine learning to discover which case attributes most strongly drive a target outcome. [m[19;3H   [38;2;248;248;242m[2m   [22mInstead of just showing correlation, it isolates the features that have the greatest statistical impact on whether a case meets the [2m[20;6H   [22moutcome you define - so you can move from "what is happening" to "why it is happening."[m
