[K
  [1mURL:[22m http://localhost:4001/mindzie_studio/calculators/ai-causal-analysis (or https://localhost:4002 for HTTPS)[K
[K
  [1mWhat[22m [1mI[22m [1madded[22m [1mto[22m [1mthe[22m [1mpage[22m [1m(sourced[22m [1mfrom[22m [38;2;177;185;249m[1mmindzieWeb/Documentation/CalculatorCausalAnalysis_User_Guide.md [m[1mand[22m [1mthe[22m [1mengine[22m [1msource[22m [1mat[22m[K
  [38;2;177;185;249m[1mmindzie.Engine.FilterAndCalculator/Calculator/AI/CausalAnalysis/[m[1m):[22m[K
[K
  1. [1mHow[22m [1mit[22m [1mcompares[22m [1mto[22m [1mRoot[22m [1mCause[22m [1mAnalysis[22m — capability table making the correlation-vs-causation contrast explicit.[K
  2. [1mAdvanced[22m [1mSettings[22m [1mtable[22m — the real defaults: Beam width 50, Max depth 3, Min cases 30, Min lift 1.2, FDR alpha 0.05, Max returned 20,[K
  Redundancy Jaccard 0.9, sampling threshold 2M.[K
  3. [1mInterpreting[22m [1mthe[22m [1mResults[22m — the four evidence badges (Causal / Likely Causal / Associated / Correlational) with an example narrative.[K
  4. [1mHow[22m [1mthe[22m [1mAlgorithm[22m [1mWorks[22m — six-stage pipeline:[K
    - Preparation + MDL-optimal outcome-aware binning for numerics[K
    - Bitmap indexing (bitwise AND for rule coverage)[K
    - Beam-search subgroup discovery with depth-1/2/3 expansion and Jaccard redundancy filter[K
    - Statistical significance: risk ratio, 95% Wilson CI, p-value, Benjamini-Hochberg FDR[K
    - Causal adjudication: Bayesian structural signal + ridge-regularised logistic-regression propensity score[K
    - Narrative generation[K
  5. [1mPerformance[22m — timing table up to 1M cases; note on deterministic Floyd's-sampling above 2M.[K
  6. [1mKnown[22m [1mLimitations[22m [1m(v1)[22m — binary outcomes only, no per-case explanations, no temporal drift split.[K
